adviseScripts.text: I've been a little spend-happy recently.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: How do I cut back on my spending and save money?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Just stop shopping.
Keep spending. When you go bankrupt, naturally you'll stop spending.
H-how can you suggest such a thing?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It's one of the few joys I have left in my life...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You should be more sensitive, Commander!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: C'mon, I'm not that much of a lost cause!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Well, maybe I will spend a little more. But I'm not going bankrupt!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I talk more with Privaty about finances.
Commander.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Would you splurge for good quality? Or do you always save money?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: The cheaper the better.
I'm fine with anything, so long as it tastes good.
Hm! I expected as much.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Spoken like someone just scraping by in a slum.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: And by 'slum', I mean your Outpost, of course.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Well, of course! That's a given!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: But it is a wise answer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It's not what I expected, so I like it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I hang out a little longer with Privaty, who is grumpy but enjoys gossiping.
Yulha's been nagging me a lot lately.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Admi's really been on my case, too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What's their problem?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It's because they like you.
It's because you're sloppy.
That's what I thought too...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Well... I can't say I feel the same way about them.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Then again, I do trust them as teammates...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: So maybe I should listen to their advice. Just a little.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Me? Sloppy?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Who are you calling sloppy?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You're full of it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I hang out a little while longer with Privaty, who pretends she doesn't like to gossip.
Commander, you have to tell the truth.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: If Rapi and I got into a fight, whose side would you take?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Yours.
Can I say Rapi?
No surprise there.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Even though you and Rapi are practically joined at the hip, you still have a soft spot for me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'll keep that in mind.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Of course not!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'm the one asking, so you have to pick me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: How can you even ask such a thing? Do you really like Rapi that much?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I spend time with a thoroughly irascible Privaty.
I ran into Yulha, but she just gave me a death glare the whole time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: She nagged me half to death, then just walked off.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'm feeling a little upset about it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Isn't that how Yulha always is?
Yulha isn't being fair to you.
You think I don't know that?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Comfort, you idiot! I want someone to comfort me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: *Sigh*
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Not really.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Yulha is just like that with everyone.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It didn't upset me that much.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: But I feel better after hearing you take my side.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I comfort Privaty, who is upset.
I think Admi may be going through puberty.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: She's been making all these heavy sighing noises lately.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I hope nothing's wrong with her.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Does she only sigh when she sees you?
Puberty is often a very perplexing thing.
Maybe? Does she?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... Wait a minute.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What does that mean?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Are you saying I'm the one that's making her feel this way?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You're right. Everyone gets a little confused when they're going through puberty.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I guess all her sighing isn't so strange.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Maybe I should start treating her more like an adult.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I chat a while longer with Privaty about Admi.
Look, I'm gonna ask you a question, but don't read too much into it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'm not even that curious! Honestly!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: But... what's your type?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Someone who's aloof and chic, but not TOO well put together.
Someone with a tough exterior, but who is sweet and innocent once you get to know them.
Huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: That sounds so dumb.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Still though, aloof and chic describes me pretty well.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'll take it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What kind of idiot...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Wait, don't tell me you like Yulha?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: That's a perfect description of her.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I argue with Privaty about what we look for in a person.
Commander, why do you want to operate on the surface?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Have you ever considered...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: working for the Central Government?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: So, you want to work more closely with me?
I'm perfectly happy being a Commander.
W-w-who says I want to work with you?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I just wanted to see if you'd ever have a change of heart, that's all!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, that's it. I'm just testing you to see whether or not you truly like the Outpost.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I knew you would say that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: That's what I've always liked about...!!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: W-wait! That's not what I meant!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I-I just meant it's good for a Commander to think that way!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I calm down the flustered Privaty.
Commander, I've made up my mind.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Starting today, I won't let what anyone else says affect me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: O-of course I've always been strong, but starting today I'll be even stronger.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: So, with that in mind, go on and try to say something that would upset me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'm dating Rapi.
Privaty, I like you.
Pssh, is that all you've got?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Trying to get my goat with such tired methods... how disappointing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You're not actually serious, are you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Um... Erm... Uhhhh!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: How can you say something like that?! That's cheating!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I spend some time chatting with Privaty.
Commander, um...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: if you were in a relationship, and went out on a date...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: where would you want to go?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: The stores on Royal Road.
A cafe in the Outpost.
Royal Road? That's unexpected.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I thought you had no interest in shopping...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Well, there's certainly plenty to see and do around Royal Road. It would be perfect for a date.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: A cafe at the Outpost?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Why on earth would you go on a date there?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I mean, sure, I like coffee, but still!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: That's not a proper date at all!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You've got to go somewhere nicer than that!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I argue with Privaty about this imaginary date.
I lucked out and managed to snag two tickets to the movies,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: but Yulha is busy and I can't seem to find Admi...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Who else could I possibly go to the movies with?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Is it okay if I go with you?
If you want me to go with you, just ask.
Sigh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I guess I'm all out of options at this point. Fine, if you want to.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What time should we meet up?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You don't think I brought this up just to get you to come along, do you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Besides, why are you eavesdropping on me when I'm talking to myself?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about movies.
If peace is one day restored up on the surface,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: what kind of life do you want to live?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'd like to spend my days raising a family.
I want to live alone in a quiet place.
F-family?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Just who exactly makes up this family?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: No, don't tell me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I knew it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: so I can't blame you for feeling that way.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: But wouldn't it be lonely being all on your own?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Before we finished our discussion, Privaty and I speculated on my future life.
I've noticed there are a lot of new TV shows and novels about forbidden love affairs between a Commander and their Nikkes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What are your thoughts, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Sounds like a fascinating plot.
I'm not too fond of it.
R-r-really?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Actually, I think it's not too bad either.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Who knows... Maybe it could even happen in real life...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Oh, really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I mean... yeah, right!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Come on, forbidden love between a Commander and a Nikke? It's absurd!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk more about forbidden love.
I'm thinking of changing my hairstyle.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I wanted to know what you think...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What kind of hairstyle do you think would suit me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Nothing could top the hairstyle you have now.
I'm not sure.
Seriously?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'll keep this hairstyle... for now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Don't get it twisted, this has nothing to do with what you just said!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Come on, throw me a bone here!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You could at least say if you like it better tied up or let down...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Forget it. I'll just leave it like this.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I spend some time thinking about new potential hairstyles for Privaty.
Your room smells nice today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I just came out of the shower.
I'm using a new air freshener.
Oh, er... then...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: That smell must be Commander's shampoo...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Gah! I mean... I was just talking to myself! Just ignore me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: R-really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Can you tell me what brand you're using?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I ended my discussion with Privaty while surrounded by a pleasant aroma.
Special occasions like a birthday or anniversary
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: can make an otherwise normal day special.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: If you were to make today as a special day, what would it be for?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Our very first time.
One of the days where we sit down and talk.
O-our first time?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: First time for what?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: S-stop filling my head with dirty thoughts!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: But we always have these discussions.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Y-you do it with all the other Nikkes too...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What makes you consider this day to be so special?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I share a special moment together.
I went shopping recently.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: How do you think this looks on me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It's perfect.
It doesn't really suit you.
Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I knew it would look good on me,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: but it's nice to hear it from someone else.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Hey! You could at least say it looks okay on me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Don't you have any common sense?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I share yet another meaningful discussion.
I've been having the worst dreams.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Have you had any memorable dreams lately?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Yes... but it'd be a bit awkward telling you about it.
No, not really.
What?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What kind of dream could it possibly be...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: D-don't tell me anything more! How embarrassing!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Yeah?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I guess there are a lot of dreams that we don't remember.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: A bit of a boring answer... although I expected as much.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about dreams.
Huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You don't look so good.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Did you not sleep well last night?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: How did you know?
Not at all, I slept great.
I'm just attentive, that's all!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It's not like I single you out for attention any more than anyone else!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... But if you're tired, we can go easy with our discussion today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Really...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You seem more tired than usual...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Well, if you say you're okay, I'll just take your word for it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I share yet another meaningful discussion.
Commander, isn't there anything you covet?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Anything that you would kill to have right now?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: No I haven't.
Maybe some new clothes... or a pair of shoes...
Ha! I envy you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I've been filled with so much desire lately, that it's honestly a little worrying.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... After we're done here, I should go shopping.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: So there is something you would like to have!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Why don't you come with me once we're done here?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Erm... by that I mean you can tag along and we can go shopping together, that's all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Privaty about various things we want.
